    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。再检查一下：LMS门户扣费-0.1，课堂服务收入+0.1，这个资金流向要清晰。提款流程中ContentCDN明确标注withdrawal，因为它是内容分发的最终结算点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "dt = -0.1",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "dt = +0.1",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
