    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式全部应用完毕。我注意到代码注释里写了\"µpay - services debit the user account for usage\"，这正好解释了核心机制。整个架构现在完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "debit",
        "service smart contract"
