      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看一眼：GradeSync在提款流程中作为Service2，但它没出现在智能合约子图里。这是故意的，GradeSync只参与结算不参与实时计费？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Service2",
        "withdrawal",
        "service smart contract"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，从代码结构看GradeSync只在withdrawal子图出现。可能成绩同步是周期性批量结算，不像课堂服务那样实时计费。这个设计合理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
